<h2 id="the-takeaway">The Takeaway</h2>

<p>If you never use <em>will</em> again, your English would sound more natural than using it every single time you talk about a future event. Thatâ€™s extreme, but if you start using present continuous and going to more often, thatâ€™s already a huge start.</p>

